openflap
by Alan Witkowski

https://github.com/jazztickets/openflap

Linux dependencies:
cmake
sdl2
sdl2-mixer
sdl2-image
sdl2-ttf

Building:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make -j`nproc`

Building in Codelite:
Open codelite/openflap.workspace with codelite. Right-click the project
(green folder icon in left sidepane) and select "Run CMake". Then build with F7.

Keys
Spacebar, mouseclick, or joystick button to jump.

Save data is in ~/.openflap.
